snippet.title: Metroid: Samus Returns - Launch Trailer (Nintendo 3DS)
snippet.description:
Samus is back! Embark on a daring mission to eliminate a hostile species in Metroid: Samus Returns, out now only on Nintendo 3DS family systems. 

#Nintendo #3DS
